OL,3,CVictim of murder plot GP opens up
OL,4,Cabout poison jab ordeal on This Morning
OL,6,FReporter Amy Sutton watched Patrick
OL,7,FO'Hara open up about the elaborate
OL,8,Fmurder plot on This Morning
OL,10,FThe victim at the centre of an
OL,11,Felaborate murder plot by his former
OL,12,Fpartner's GP son has opened up about
OL,13,Fhis ordeal.
OL,15,FPatrick O'Hara was poisoned by Thomas
OL,16,FKwan, who disguised himself as a
OL,17,Fcommunity nurse administering a Covid
OL,18,Fbooster in his Newcastle home, in a
OL,19,Frouse to fast-track his inheritance.
