OL,3,CVictim of murder plot GP opens up
OL,4,Cabout poison jab ordeal on This Morning
OL,6,FLast month Kwan, of Ingleby Barwick,
OL,7,Fnear Stockton, was jailed for 31 years
OL,8,Ffor attempted murder.
OL,10,FSpeaking on This Morning on Monday (9
OL,11,FDecember), Mr O'Hara recalled the
OL,12,Fattack in January this year and the
OL,13,Flasting impact it has had on his
OL,14,Fphysical and mental health.
OL,16,FThe 72-year-old described the moment
OL,17,FKwan's needle containing poison
OL,18,Fentered his arm as "indescribable" and
OL,19,Fsaid he immediately suspected his now
OL,20,Fformer partner Jenny Leung's son.
