OL,6,F"He put all his stuff away and went
OL,7,Fout the house, and Jenny came down and
OL,8,Fsaid 'oh he looked like the same
OL,9,Fheight as my son'," he explained. "So
OL,10,FI went out the door after him to see
OL,11,Fif I could unmask him but he was away."
OL,13,FAsked by presenter Ben Shephard if he
OL,14,Fwas suspicious, he said "straight
OL,15,Faway", adding: "He was the only one
OL,16,Fwho could have medically done
OL,17,Fsomething like take blood and
OL,18,Feverything else.
OL,20,F"And he's the only one I've had an
OL,21,Faltercation with over all the years."
