OL,3,CVictim of murder plot GP opens up
OL,4,Cabout poison jab ordeal on This Morning
OL,6,FNewcastle Crown Court previously heard
OL,7,Fthat 53-year-old Kwan hatched a plan
OL,8,Fto kill the long-term partner of his
OL,9,Fmother in a bid to cut him out of her
OL,10,Fwill.
OL,12,FMs Leung's will stated that Mr O'Hara
OL,13,Fcould remain living in her property
OL,14,Ffollowing her death - something which
OL,15,Fprosecutors said struck at the heart
OL,16,Fof Kwan's sense of entitlement.
