OL,6,FMr O'Hara told This Morning presenters
OL,7,FBen Shephard and Cat Deeley that Kwan
OL,8,Fand his mother had already become
OL,9,Fsomewhat estranged over conflict
OL,10,Frelating to inheritance and finances.
OL,12,FHe added that there was therefore
OL,13,F"irony" in the fact his relationship
OL,14,Fwith Ms Leung was coming to an end
OL,15,Fwhen Kwan launched his attack.
OL,17,FMr O'Hara also agreed that the
OL,18,Fattempted murder became the "catalyst"
OL,19,Fin bringing him and his ex-wife back
OL,20,Ftogether.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
