OL,6,FHe said Ms Leung, who he met while
OL,7,Fworking at Marks and Spencer more than
OL,8,F20 years ago during something of a
OL,9,Fpossible "mid-life crisis", had moved
OL,10,Fout of her Newcastle home and was now
OL,11,Fliving with her daughter in Hong Kong.
OL,13,FThe murder plot victim said he was
OL,14,Fstill in touch with Ms Leung and held
OL,15,Fno ill feelings towards Kwan, as he
OL,16,Fbelieved "justice was done".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
