OL,3,CVictim of murder plot GP opens up
OL,4,Cabout poison jab ordeal on This Morning
OL,6,F"At the time, I felt really against
OL,7,Fhim, but time's a great healer and
OL,8,Fwhen I was lying in bed, I just
OL,9,Fthought it's wasted time...I don't
OL,10,Fhate him," he said.
OL,12,F"It's happened and the justice was
OL,13,Fdone. I was happy that justice was
OL,14,Fcarried out and that's the way it
OL,15,Fshould have been."
OL,17,FMr O'Hara was left requiring multiple
OL,18,Foperations and a stint in intensive
OL,19,Fcare.
