OL,6,FAs well as physical injuries, the
OL,7,Fattack also had a significant effect
OL,8,Fon the grandfather's mental health. He
OL,9,Ftold This Morning viewers he lost his
OL,10,Fhair, experienced delirium and
OL,11,Fdebilitating fatigue.
OL,13,FDespite this, the mad-keen golfer, who
OL,14,Fhas enjoyed playing in Scotland for
OL,15,Fmore than 30 years, said he had been
OL,16,Fback on the driving range.
OL,18,F"Everybody thought I couldn't do it
OL,19,Fand they already had a substitute for
OL,20,Fus but I managed to push myself (to
OL,21,Fget back to it)," he added.
